The Form has the following fields/sections:

[emph]Name[/emph]

Text: the name of the Role.


[emph]Access[/emph]

It is a listing of all Project-modules (non Global ones), each one occupies one row.
For each module there are 4 checkboxes: Read, Write, Create and Admin. Each one occupies a column.
So, you decide what permissions have to be checked on each row.
